sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Investor
  participant Doc as Document Service
  participant S3 as S3/MinIO
  participant Scanner as DigiLocker/Scanner
  participant N8N
  participant Node as Node Verification API
  participant Audit as Audit/Event
  Investor->>Doc: Request upload intent
  Doc->>S3: Create signed upload URL
  Investor->>S3: Upload binary
  Investor->>Doc: Confirm upload metadata
  Doc->>Audit: document.uploaded audit/event
  Scanner->>N8N: Verification callback
  N8N->>Node: Safe verification payload
  Node->>Doc: Update verification status through service
  Node->>Audit: document.verified or document.rejected
